\id PHM - Urat NT (PNGBTA); Hilkka Arminen (SIL Advisor); 25-Nov-2015; 1-FEB-2016 
\h FILEMON 
\toc3 Flm 
\toc2 Filemon 
\toc1 Pol nainge tup nal me Filemon 
\mt2 Pol nainge tup nal me  
\mt1 Filemon  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1-2  \x - \xo 1.1-2 \xt Kol 4.17\x*Ŋam Pol, ŋam marp moto mwahupwaiꞌe me naŋ tikin Jisas Krais. Ŋam topoꞌe toꞌ poi Timoti, poi hindi member tup eꞌe malme nin. Wusyep eꞌe nal me nin Filemon, wah ilyeh topoꞌe ŋimei poi. Topoꞌe nal lenge mitiŋ ŋaiye ŋoihmbwaip teŋeime Jisas ŋaiye jahilyeh yarp yokoh nin, topoꞌe mihyen poi Apia, topoꞌe wah ilyeh poi Arkipus ŋaiye taꞌe miyeꞌ wondoh ŋaiye ya lalme murmbe mambaꞌe lenge mitiŋ menge mutme Jisas Krais.  
\v 3 Poi manange wusyep malme me Yai Got hindi Lahmborenge poi Jisas Krais ŋaiye ka ŋoihginirme yip, topoꞌe yul yip ŋoihmbwaip ŋumwaiye.   
\s1 Pol hriphrip me ŋoihmbwaip bwore tikin Filemon  
\p
\v 4 Nye nyermbe ŋupe ŋaiye ŋam misilihme Got me nin pe, ŋam hriphrip me Got.  
\v 5 Detale, ŋam si masande nange ŋoihmbwaip nin teŋeime Lahmborenge Jisas bongol sekete, topoꞌe nin ŋende nihararme lenge miyeꞌ tuweinge tikin Got.  
\v 6 Ŋam manange misilihme Got ŋaiye ka ende bongolme bilip uku ŋaiye sai me nin topoꞌe poi no, na sisyeme bworerme ŋaiꞌe ŋaiꞌe bwore bwore ŋaiye poi mambaꞌe matme Jisas Krais.  
\v 7 Toꞌ ŋam, nin si ŋende ŋoihmbwaip lenge miyeꞌ tuweinge tikin Got hriphrip supule. Ŋoihmbwaip nin ŋaiye ŋende nihararme tinge pwale hriphrip ŋembere sekete, topoꞌe plihe ŋende bongol me ŋam.   
\s1 Pol ŋisilihme Filemon nange ka ende miꞌ me Onesimus  
\p
\v 8 Ki taꞌe ŋaiye poi berei wim ilyeh tikin Krais pe, tatame ŋaiye ma mini nin wusyep bongol ŋaiye na ende ŋainde.  
\v 9 Ŋam Pol, tukwini ŋam miyeꞌ borenge pe, ŋam marp ma moto mwahupwaiꞌe me naŋ tikin Jisas. Ŋam masande nin nom, ŋai tikin ŋam misilih nin.  
\v 10  \x - \xo 1.10 \xt Kol 4.9\x*Taꞌe luku pe, ŋam misilih nin ŋaiye na ungwisme talah ŋam Onesimus. Detale, ŋupe ŋaiye ŋam marp mwahupwaiꞌe me naŋ tikin Jisas Krais pe, ŋam taꞌe yai kin, detale, kin si tahar Kristen.  
\v 11 Somohonme yukur ki ŋende ŋainde bwore ŋaiye ka ungwisme nin, pakai. Kom tukwini kin si ŋende wah bwore ŋaiye ka ungwisme nin topoꞌe ŋam.  
\v 12 Tukwini ŋam plihe member kin mala mil me nin pe, ŋoihmbwaip ŋam iki kin nenge nal no.  
\v 13 Ŋam da mupwaiꞌe kin ŋaiye ya hindi murp eꞌe no, ka ambaꞌe luh nin ŋaiye ka ungwisme ŋam ŋupe ŋaiye ŋam marp mwahupwaiꞌe me wusyep bwore tikin Got.  
\v 14 Kom ŋam gwarnge ŋaiye ma mututus nin nange na ungwisme ŋam. Kut ŋam masande nange na ende tuꞌe ŋaiye ŋasande nin. Taꞌe luku pe, yukur ma mende ŋainde tutume ŋaiye na tapam ilyeh topoꞌe ŋam.  
\v 15 Mise, Onesimus kin garnge nin nal sikirp gwaingwaiye, kom tukwini kin si nat pe, plihe ambaꞌe kin enge ot ŋaiye pa hindi yurp ilyeh nye nyermbe.  
\v 16 Tukwini kin yukur miyeꞌ wah pakaiye, pakai. Kin si tahar Kristen pe, ŋam mende nihararme kin taꞌe ŋaiye toꞌ ŋam ende. Kom tukwini ŋam sisyeme ŋaiye na ende nihararme kin tuꞌe miyeꞌ wah pakaiye, topoꞌe plihe nato Krais pe, kin taꞌe ŋaiye toꞌ nin bwore mise kili.   
\p
\v 17 Taꞌe luku pe, ŋaiye na ŋoiheryembe ŋam tuꞌe ŋimei nin pe, na plihe ende nihararme kin ŋahilyeh tuꞌe ŋaiye nin ŋende nihararme ŋam ŋupe ŋaiye ka otme nin.  
\v 18 O ŋaiye Onesimus ka ende ŋainde pupwa me nin, lakai wuyah nin ende ka si me kin pe, plihe bunjenge ember naŋ ŋam Pol el guh wuyah kin uku.  
\v 19 Ŋam Pol, syep ŋam eꞌe ŋam mainge wusyep malme nin. Yukur ma mininge pakai me wuyah nin ŋaiye sai me ŋam, se ma mungwisme. Topoꞌe ŋam tatame ŋaiye ma mininge na, wuyah ŋam sai me nin ŋaiye na ungwisme. Wuyah nin teŋeime ŋam pe, wuyah uku ki laip nin. Detale, ŋam mungwis me nin ŋaiye nin tahar Kristen.  
\v 20 Taꞌe luku pe, toꞌ ŋam, nato naŋ tikin Lahmborenge pe, ŋam masande ŋaiye na ende ŋoihmbwaip bwore otme ŋam. Detale, poi berei hoime miyeꞌ tikin Krais.   
\p
\v 21 Ŋupe ŋaiye ŋam mainge wusyep eꞌe pe, ŋam si sisyeme nange se na ende gunde wusyep mune ŋaiye ŋam mana nin. Topoꞌe ŋaimune ŋaiye na ende me Onesimus pe, se na ende usungurhme wusyep ŋaiye ŋam mana nin.  
\v 22 Topoꞌe ende miꞌmiꞌ me dou ende nato yokoh ŋaiye ka si me ŋam ŋaiye ma muta mambaꞌe posoh. Ŋam sisyeme nange Got se ka usyunde yisilih yip pe, se ka ember ŋam ŋaiye ma muta metekeꞌ yip.  
\v 23  \x - \xo 1.23 \xt Kol 1.7, 4.12\x*Epafras, miyeꞌ ŋaiye poi hindi hoime marp mwahupwaiꞌe me naŋ tikin Jisas Krais, nember nin wusyep hriphrip kin,  
\v 24  \x - \xo 1.24 \xt Apo 12.12,25, 13.13, 15.37-39, 19.29, 27.2, Kol 4.10,14, 2Ti 4.10-11\x*topoꞌme lenge miyeꞌ wah ilyeh ŋam Mak pe, Aristarkus pe, Demas topoꞌe Luk.  
\v 25 Ŋam de ma misilihme Got ŋaiye ŋoihmbwaip ŋumwaiye tikin Lahmborenge Jisas Krais ka si topoꞌme yip lalme.   